OL,6,GLast year, Clean Feed reported on
OL,7,Gplans to update the BBC News globe
OL,8,Gbranding, created by designer Martin
OL,9,GLambie-Nairn and implemented back in
OL,10,G2008.
OL,12,FIt is our understanding there was a
OL,13,Fplan to have a new look ready to go
OL,14,Flive by April this year, in time for
OL,15,Fthe merger of the BBC News Channel
OL,16,Fand BBC World News.
OL,18,FFor various reasons ` cost being a
OL,19,Fsignificant factor ` those plans are
OL,20,Fon hold for the time being.
OL,3,CPresentation changes coming up on BBC
OL,4,CNews
