OL,6,FUpdated countdown sequences have been
OL,7,Fproduced.
OL,9,FBBC Breakfast is expected to get new
OL,10,Ftitles later this year and will also
OL,11,Fadopt the Chameleon template (blocks
OL,12,Ftop, 'NEWS' bottom). The programme is
OL,13,Fexpected to move to its new studio
OL,14,Faround late-spring.
OL,16,FA new graphics template for non-news
OL,17,Fprogramming such as Click is also
OL,18,Fbeing developed.  This will be rolled
OL,19,Fout gradually.
